divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside smoking a cigarette on my back deck at night when i saw something bright coming above the trees. It looked like a moving star about the size of jupiter that started rising aboving the trees going faster than an airplane that was a solid white light. It had no blinking lights that indicated it was an airplane or helicopter. I know there was an airforce base east of where i was, but it couldnt have been a jet or stealth bomber. It left my eye sight as it moved past our house going in the opposite direction of the moon.
Summary: Watching a star like object shoot fast above the trees past the moon.
